1520
01:25:39,812 --> 01:25:41,051
you still stayed with me

1521
01:25:41,612 --> 01:25:42,691
in the Dragon Clan.

1522
01:25:45,252 --> 01:25:46,091
In the third life,

1523
01:25:46,812 --> 01:25:48,051
we wandered the mortal realm.

1524
01:25:48,932 --> 01:25:50,531
You didn’t remember who you were,

1525
01:25:50,532 --> 01:25:51,531
but were still willing to

1526
01:25:52,452 --> 01:25:53,451
