1531
01:26:05,212 --> 01:26:06,651
I’m merging the bloodlines

1532
01:26:07,052 --> 01:26:07,971
of the Dragon Clan and Celestial Clan—

1533
01:26:08,932 --> 01:26:09,651
from now on,

1534
01:26:10,332 --> 01:26:11,171
there shall be no Celestial Clan.

1535
01:26:12,252 --> 01:26:14,091
Think of it as my revenge

1536
01:26:14,652 --> 01:26:15,371
for my parents and people.

1537
01:26:15,972 --> 01:26:16,651
Dragon Xian,

1538
01:26:17,812 --> 01:26:19,491
I won’t allow you to vanish like this.

1539
01:26:20,892 --> 01:26:22,651
We share memories of three lifetimes—

1540
01:26:23,092 --> 01:26:24,571
I’ve finally recalled them all.

1541
01:26:25,412 --> 01:26:26,251
And now you’re willing

1542
01:26:27,452 --> 01:26:28,891
